Build:
  in this directory,
     mkdir build
     cd build
     cmake ..
     make

Synopsis:
  ./cascade <options>

Description:
  This program will continually detect objects in the image at the given path,
  and output a count to a file, as well as a debug image.

  --image-path <image path>
    image to run the cascade detector on
    (default: build/detect.jpg)

  --dgb-image-path <image path>
    debug image showing detection bounding boxes
    (default: build/dbg.jpg)

  --count-path <count path>
    file to output the detection count to
    (default: build/count.dat)

  --cascade-path <cascade path>
    prelearned opencv cascade classifier
    (default: build/haarcascades/haarcascade_frontalface_alt.xml)